## 📊 YOUR REPOSITORY: hyperbolic-semantic-networks

**Namespace:** hyperbolic-semantic  
**ClusterQueue:** hyperbolic-semantic  
**Resources:** 30% (fMRI/EEG analysis heavy!)

**Allocation:**
- RAM: 150Gi nominal (borrowing up to 300Gi)
- CPU: 18 cores nominal (borrowing up to 36)
- GPU: 1x L4 (shared, for hyperbolic embeddings + fMRI)
- Storage: 2TB (1TB nvme-fast + 1TB hdd-bulk)

**Workloads:**
- fMRI analysis (4D volumes, GLM, connectivity)
- EEG analysis (if integrated with pcs-meta-repo)
- Hyperbolic embeddings (Poincaré, Lorentz - GPU accelerated!)
- Large-scale graph processing
- Statistical bootstrap (permutation tests)

