## 💾 STORAGE

**Active fMRI/EEG datasets:**
```yaml
storageClassName: t560-nvme-fast  # 7000 MB/s!
```

**Archives, results:**
```yaml
storageClassName: t560-hdd-bulk  # 500 MB/s
```

**Semantic graphs (shared):**
```yaml
storageClassName: nfs-shared  # 3TB Pegasus R4
```

