## 🎯 GPU USAGE

**Hyperbolic embeddings (Poincaré disk, Lorentz):**
- Riemannian optimization benefits from GPU (10-100x speedup!)
- Request GPU in job manifest:
```yaml
resources:
  requests:
    nvidia.com/gpu: 1
    memory: 64Gi
```

